_header: What should me cause or any wise to think
_description: A Compleynt — three stanzas rhyme royal

BodFair16.First Lines:
What shuld me cause or ony wyse to thynkTo haue plesaunce or Ioy in
                    any kynde…
BodFair16.Last Lines:
…But I that am not worthy to be blamydMe thynke yt wrong thus
                    for to be dyffamed
